OL,5, Peloton is recalling more than two     
OL,6, million exercise bikes over concerns   
OL,7, that the seat assembly could break     
OL,8, during use and injure customers.       
OL,10,FOwners have been advised to immediately
OL,11,Fstop using the bikes and contact       
OL,12,FPeloton for a free repair.             
OL,14,FThe company has received numerous      
OL,15,Freports of injuries including "a       
OL,16,Ffractured wrist and lacerations" after 
OL,17,Fthe bike's seat detached during use.   
OL,19,FThe recall applies to bikes soldin the 
OL,20,FUS from January 2018 through May 2023. 
